A plugin for rails that gives you control of the html <meta> tags on a application/controller/action basis. 

Controllers
-----------


Helpers
-------

<code>
<%= meta\_tag :title %>
\# Should render as
\# <meta name="title" content="Woo, the Internet!!!" />
</code>

<pre>
<%= meta\_tags %>
\# Should render all the meta tags defined
\# <meta name="title" content="Woo, the Internet!!!" />
\# <meta name="description" content="bla, bla, bla" />
\# <meta name="keywords" content="key1, key2, key3" />
</pre>

Inspired by [merb_meta](http://github.com/coryodaniel/merb_meta)